ch.bfh.bti7081.s2016.blue.hv.entities

Class DrugOrderItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • ch.bfh.bti7081.s2016.blue.hv.entities.BaseEntity
      • ch.bfh.bti7081.s2016.blue.hv.entities.DrugOrderItem
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    @Entity
public class DrugOrderItem
extends BaseEntity
    The DrugOrderItem is a wrapper class for Drug objects to be added to a DrugOrder. It inherits the basic fields and methods from the BaseEntity class. DrugOrderItems are persisted with their corresponding DrugOrder (cascade all).
    Author:
    Michel Hosmann
